},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7fa34df3-0a73-4f8f-806d-4a5f5107d46e","uuid":"1d044362-55e5-49dd-835f-12f342ba7e50","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:31:10.487Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"A  tests/__init__.py\nA  tests/test_game.py\nA  tests/test_words.py\nA  word_garden/__init__.py\nA  word_garden/game.py\nA  word_garden/words.py\n--- check nothing bad staged ---\nclean staged set","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}},{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_01ANvq26HhFWRa1RyuwCBKF8","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01RwniYLAKQ3gHqYDuU6nJdU","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git commit -q -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\nImplement Word Garden core engine: words, game logic, tests\n\nPure stdlib game engine (no UI) per SPEC sections 6-8, 12-14, 16.\n\n- words.py: WORDS list, difficulty table encoded once, select_word(rng)\n  filters by length band and water_for() returns starting water; unknown\n  difficulty or empty pool raises ValueError; default rng uses module random.\n- game.py: GameState dataclass (exact field order), new_game, validate_guess\n  (no state access), apply_guess (correct/wrong/repeat/game-over), display_word,\n  is_won/is_lost. User-facing messages are module-level constants.\n- tests: 31 cases covering SPEC section 16 with positive full-outcome\n  assertions and seeded random.Random for determinism.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n)\" && git log --oneline -1","description":"Commit the engine and tests"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":330,"cache_read_input_tokens":47993,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":330},"output_tokens":54,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7fa34df3-0a73-4f8f-806d-4a5f5107d46e","uuid":"ba2a1f51-cf17-4161-a2f4-83ce381e1401","request_id":"req_011CbxfCVtk95yhmexnsVp2r"},{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01RwniYLAKQ3gHqYDuU6nJdU","type":"tool_result","content":"a9d818e Implement Word Garden core engine: words, game logic, tests","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7fa34df3-0a73-4f8f-806d-4a5f5107d46e","uuid":"c38090e7-2236-4a4c-94a3-2631daa069af","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:31:16.879Z","tool_use_result":{"stdout":"a9d818e Implement Word Garden core engine: words, game logic, tests","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false}},{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_01WwCU2PMCA7a7uQcaZH8Wsh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. The Word Garden core engine is implemented, tested, and committed on `task-001-w5`.\n\n## What shipped\n\n**`word_garden/words.py`** — `WORDS` (the 10-word SPEC list, uppercase), `select_word(difficulty, rng=None)`, `water_for(difficulty)`. The difficulty table (water + length band) is encoded **once** in `DIFFICULTIES`. `rng=None` uses the module-level `random` (production stays non-deterministic); unknown difficulty *and* an empty filtered pool both raise `ValueError` (never a silent fallback).\n\n**`word_garden/game.py`** — `GameState` dataclass with the exact SPEC §12 field order; `new_game`, `validate_guess` (state-free; repeat detection lives in `apply_guess`), `apply_guess` (correct / wrong / repeat / post-game-over no-op, with win/loss flagging), `display_word`, `is_won`, `is_lost`. All user-facing strings are module-level constants imported by the tests.\n\n**`tests/`** — 31 tests covering all UI-free SPEC §16 cases with **positive full-outcome** assertions (e.g. a wrong guess asserts water −1 *and* weeds +1 *and* letter recorded *and* the exact message) and seeded `random.Random` for determinism.\n\n## Acceptance verification\n- `python3 -m unittest discover -s tests` → **31 passed**\n- `python3 -m compileall -q word_garden` → **green**\n- No `input()`/`print()` anywhere in `word_garden/`\n- Stdlib only; no bytecode staged; `SPEC.md`/`farnsworth.json`/`tasks/`/`.code-tips.md` untouched\n\nOne open design choice I made under the focus directive: `apply_guess` mutates and returns the **same** `GameState` (rather than a copy) — consistent with the `-> GameState` signature and the simplest faithful reading of SPEC §6. The task-002 UI can rely on that. Win/loss `status_message` constants reuse the SPEC §6.6/6.7 wording as single-line feedback (the full multi-line screens are UI, task-002)."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":436,"cache_read_input_tokens":48323,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":436},"output_tokens":4,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7fa34df3-0a73-4f8f-806d-4a5f5107d46e","uuid":"b9468de3-fd08-4540-9d90-d0ab41f0a1b4","request_id":"req_011CbxfCy4NidroVn3FR7e4A"},{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":200327,"duration_api_ms":203643,"ttft_ms":1993,"ttft_stream_ms":1992,"time_to_request_ms":52,"num_turns":14,"result":"Done. The Word Garden core engine is implemented, tested, and committed on `task-001-w5`.\n\n## What shipped\n\n**`word_garden/words.py`** — `WORDS` (the 10-word SPEC list, uppercase), `select_word(difficulty, rng=None)`, `water_for(difficulty)`. The difficulty table (water + length band) is encoded **once** in `DIFFICULTIES`. `rng=None` uses the module-level `random` (production stays non-deterministic); unknown difficulty *and* an empty filtered pool both raise `ValueError` (never a silent fallback).\n\n**`word_garden/game.py`** — `GameState` dataclass with the exact SPEC §12 field order; `new_game`, `validate_guess` (state-free; repeat detection lives in `apply_guess`), `apply_guess` (correct / wrong / repeat / post-game-over no-op, with win/loss flagging), `display_word`, `is_won`, `is_lost`. All user-facing strings are module-level constants imported by the tests.\n\n**`tests/`** — 31 tests covering all UI-free SPEC §16 cases with **positive full-outcome** assertions (e.g. a wrong guess asserts water −1 *and* weeds +1 *and* letter recorded *and* the exact message) and seeded `random.Random` for determinism.\n\n## Acceptance verification\n- `python3 -m unittest discover -s tests` → **31 passed**\n- `python3 -m compileall -q word_garden` → **green**\n- No `input()`/`print()` anywhere in `word_garden/`\n- Stdlib only; no bytecode staged; `SPEC.md`/`farnsworth.json`/`tasks/`/`.code-tips.md` untouched\n\nOne open design choice I made under the focus directive: `apply_guess` mutates and returns the **same** `GameState` (rather than a copy) — consistent with the `-> GameState` signature and the simplest faithful reading of SPEC §6. The task-002 UI can rely on that. Win/loss `status_message` constants reuse the SPEC §6.6/6.7 wording as single-line feedback (the full multi-line screens are UI, task-002).","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"7fa34df3-0a73-4f8f-806d-4a5f5107d46e","total_cost_usd":1.0396275,"usage":{"input_tokens":4878,"cache_creation_input_tokens":33426,"cache_read_input_tokens":518697,"output_tokens":16747,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":33426,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":2,"output_tokens":730,"cache_read_input_tokens":48323,"cache_creation_input_tokens":436,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":436},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-8":{"inputTokens":4878,"outputTokens":16747,"cacheReadInputTokens":518697,"cacheCreationInputTokens":33426,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.0366734999999998,"contextWindow":1000000,"maxOutputTokens":64000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":2874,"outputTokens":16,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.002954,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[{"tool_name":"Bash","tool_use_id":"toolu_01YJPhE6he2MKsghGReM1Kiz","tool_input":{"command":"python3 - <<'EOF'\nWORDS = [\"GARDEN\",\"FLOWER\",\"PLANET\",\"PYTHON\",\"TERMINAL\",\"MEADOW\",\"ORCHARD\",\"VINEYARD\",\"SEEDLING\",\"HARVEST\"]\nbands = {\"easy\":(4,6),\"normal\":(5,8),\"hard\":(7,None)}\nfor d,(lo,hi) in bands.items():\n    pool=[w for w in WORDS if len(w)>=lo and (hi is None or len(w)<=hi)]\n    print(d, [(w,len(w)) for w in pool])\nEOF","description":"Verify non-empty pools per difficulty"}}],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"162ad3ad-2e95-4405-96be-61946796d21e"}]
